# Publish output: regenerable from source via bench/publish-baseline.sh.
# Multi-megabyte wasm; never committed.
bench/publish/

# bench/results/ is DELIBERATELY NOT ignored. Those JSON files are the measured
# evidence behind BENCH.md -- the whole point of the baseline. Ignoring them was
# the reproducibility gap flagged as BENCH.md open reserve #4.
#
# No pattern here on purpose: `bench/results/*` followed by `!bench/results/*.json`
# does NOT work, because git cannot re-include a file whose parent directory is
# excluded -- it silently dropped every file under bench/results/final-warm/.
